properties.title: Attractions

properties.text: ARTICLE

properties.title: Living at the farmhouse we get to enjoy all the activities and attractions available in our area. Therefore we decided to let you in on our absolute favourites. Wether it is where to get the best cup of coffee, what to do on rainy days or where to eat out with your kids – we have collected our best tips for an eventful vacation at Lustrup Farmhouse right here.

properties.text: One of Porsborgs delicious courses.

Where is the best place to eat out with kids?

Our daughter’s favourite restaurant Pinocchio serves great pizzas, pasta and child friendly dishes. And they have really good ice cream desserts!

 

Nice places to shop in and around Ribe?

Sct. peder is a nice craft shop and café which serves brunch, lunch and home made baked goods.

The shop Fröken in Ribe sells life style and modern clothing for women. https://www.instagram.com/frokenribe/?hl=da

Maude Retro & Design has a wide selection of second hand interior decor.

Visit the Det Gamle Apotek if you are looking for gift ideas.

Lustrup Farmhouse Marked is our own pop-up marked with focus on lovely second hand treasures, upcycled decor for your home and garden, flea marked finds, beautiful crafts, flowers and creative ideas.

 

Here are the best beaches

Rømø beach is 35 min away by car and a great choice for an all day activity for the whole family. Fanø beach is 1 hour 15 minutes away by car – stop by Esbjerg along the way or spend the whole day building sand castles on the beach.

 

In the fall you should…

Put on your wellies and explore the Wadden Sea’s nature treasures, especially the west beach on Rømø. Watch the tide rise and fall and drink hot cocoa and coffee at Café Dax.

Take a stroll around the old cobbled streets of Ribe, see the beautiful well restored houses and visit Ribe Cathedral.

 

Cycling paths

3 recommended routes:

The Wadden Sea route is 28 km:

Around Fanø

Lustrup to Ribe 2.3 km

 

Here are our favourite animal attractions

Seal and bird expedition on Mandø, Rømø and Fanø lets you see the animals in their natural habitat where they thrive and mate.

The Wadden Sea national park is unique with its harsh and beautiful nature, rich bird life and many experiences to explore all year around.

Where can I find a nice place for a walk?

The path to Ribe City from our farmhouse is 2.3 km and takes about 30 minutes and is very cozy. The path allows a smooth ride for both baby carriages and bicycles.

 

Where is the best place for a romantic dinner or lunch?

Porsborgs by the cathedral in Ribe serves lovely food and has a nice take away menu to bring home in case you want to eat at the farmhouse.

 

Terpager Cafe by Skibbroen in Ribe serves small courses / snacks and the BEST coffee in town.

 

Queedens Gård is casual and cozy and hosts live music events and both indoor and outdoor dining. Take a seat in the rose garden and enjoy the beautiful climbing wines and roses.

Rainy days? Here are our favourite indoor activities

Go to the Wadden Sea Center to explore the exhibitions or visit the many museums of Ribe. Invite the family to Fiskeri- & Søfartsmuseet; a genuine maritime family attraction for both kids and adults. Are you also a lego lover? Go visit Lego House in Billund, only an hour drive from the farmhouse or bring the bathing suits to the water park in Esbjerg

 

What are the best activities for kids?

We love to bring our daughter Ella Rose to WOW Funpark in Billund or Skjern, it is a nature playground with tree top climbs and much more. Legoland and Lego House are our absolute favourite parks to visit. A trip to the beach followed by a huge ice cream cone makes us happy and if we want to see animals we go to one of the many zoo’s in the area.

 

In the summer time you should…

Go to the beach, bring the kids’ shovels and bukets and build sand castles all day.  On windy days it’s fun to bring a kite.
Alex and Ella Rose on the swings at Lego House.

Here you can experience unique nature

A trip to Mandø lets you experience nature up close. Perfect for bird watching and seal safari. We recommend ending the day with a Vadehavsplatter for dinner.

Take a walk along the beautiful beach on the island of Rømø and search for amber at the shoreline.

The natural phenomenon Black Sun occurs every spring and fall where thousands of starlings dance in the sky. Guided tours can be booked.

Go pick oysters directly from the amazing scenic landscape of the Wadden Sea.

 

Recommended guided tours

Check out the website of the Wadden Sea Center which has a wide variety of guided tours. vadehavscentret.dk
Experience the spectacle of the starlings’ dance across the sky.

properties.text:
Renovating an old barn was challenging, but finally we were ready to welcome guests.  So exciting!  We were inspired by the beautiful farmhouses in England and wanted to include some of Alex’s heritage in the apartments; we therefore integrated some of the ‘farmhouse’ furniture that we had brought from England with items we had found locally.  By combining ‘old English’ and Danish influences we wanted to create a unique and cosy environment for our guests to enjoy.

 

We now welcome guests from all over the world to Lustrup Farmhouse and strive to make this a home away from home where our guests can relax, unwind and truly enjoy quality time with family, friends and loved ones.

 

Thank you for reading our story.

 

Janni, Alex, Ella Rose & Pudsey (our lovely black Labrador)
From start to finish.

From the beginning we know that we wanted to minimise our impact on the environment and make the development as environmentally sustainable as possible by using the natural resources the countryside provided.
properties.title: Let’s make it environmentally sustainable.

properties.text: The current farmhouse and outbuildings were built in 1927 as a working cattle farm. The farmhouse sits in the beautiful countryside on the outskirts of Ribe within the Wadden Sea National Park. The farmhouse has been in the family for over thirty years and two generations.
properties.title:
From farm
to farmhouse.

properties.text: We therefore retained as much of the original structure of the barn as we could and at the same time incorporated solar panels for electricity and a ground source under floor heating system.  We also wanted to encourage our guests to use our recycling facilities.
properties.title: Solar Panels & Ground Heating

properties.text:
Our dream of transforming the barn into apartments became a reality when the renovations started in September 2017. The renovation works were completed in April 2018 and we opened our doors to our first guests in May of that year.

 

Both Alex & I (Janni) really loved living in England; however, we had for some time dreamt of a change in lifestyle which would give us a better balance between work & home life. Our daughter was young and we wanted more quality time as a family. We moved to Denmark just before Christmas in 2017 to begin a new and exciting chapter in our life and that was the beginning of our dreams for Lustrup Farmhouse.

 

Lustrup Farmhouse is now our family home and the apartments are a unique destination for guests to relax, unwind and enjoy.

Project Farmhouse

The Renovation

Alle kan benytte et fælles vaskerum med vaskemaskine, tørretumbler,  strygejern, strygebræt og fryser. 

 

Ankomst og afrejse:
check-in fra kl. 15.00 paa ankomstdagen og check-ud kl 10.00 på afrejsedagen.    Bookinger i højsæson er min 4 overnatninger. Udenfor højsæsonen tilbyder Lustrup Farmhouse bookinger paa minimun 2 overnatninger.

 

Booking
Ens booking er garanteret når betaling er modtaget og gæsten har modtaget en bekræftigelse via email.

 

Afbestilling: I forbindelse med sygdom eller dødsfald i den nærmeste familie:                                          
Mere end 30 dage før ankomst: 100% af opholdets værdi refunderes.
Ved 30-14 dage før ankomst: 50% af opholdets værdi afregnes.
Mindre end 14 dage til ankomst eller hvis opholdet afbrydes: Hele opholdet afregnes.

 

Force Majeure:
Såfremt lejemålet forhindres pga. force majeure (naturkatastrofer, strejker o. lign.) er Lustrup Farmhouse ikke erstatningspligtig.

 

Internet:
Der er WIFI internet i alle ferielejligheder. Kode udleveres ved check-in.

 

Lejers ansvar:
Lejer hæfter for ferieboligens inventar. Skader påført under opholdet, afregnes ved afrejse. Boligen efterlades i opryddet stand.
